- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the performance of a specific operation (Spatial Reuse) in IEEE 802.11ax WLANs. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper discusses the potential gains in network performance through the use of SR. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper may consider the impact of SR on multimedia traffic. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the impact of SR on system performance and control. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on security or cryptography, but it may touch upon these topics in the context of WLANs.
